[normal]First Consultation Paper
[normal].  However, we are concerned that the inadequacy of the evi
[normal]dence for reform is compounded by the short treatment of the consultation in 
[normal]Next Steps, 
[normal]specifically, in Annex B
[normal].  
[normal]The analysis of the concerns expressed by many of the consultation responses, including members of the senior judiciary and public authoriti
[normal]es who will be affected by these changes
[normal],
[normal] is cursory.
